text: I, Daniel Blake is a 2016 British French Belgian drama movie directed by Ken Loach and starring Dave Johns, Hayley Squires, Kate Rutter, Sharon Percy, Gavin Webster, Kema Sikazwe and won Palme d'Or of Cannes Film Festival in 2016. ==Other websites== * Category:2016 drama movies Category:British drama movies Category:French drama movies Category:Belgian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Ken Loach
title: I, Daniel Blake
